neon lights, high gloss, premium material detail.\n\n**05. POSTER 05 | CRAFTSMANSHIP (DISPLAY)**\n*   **Page Function**: Highlight the smart features.\n*   **Visual Description**: Close up on the black central island. The blue \"96\" LED is bright and sharp. The power button has a subtle gleam.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Center Title: \"智能数显\" / \"SMART MONITOR\".\n    *   Description: \"电量一目了然 / Battery level at a glance\".\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Close-up of [glossy black panel with blue 7-segment LED battery display showing number 96], distinct circular power button, high tech feel, dark environment.\n\n**06. POSTER 06 | FUNCTION (POWER)**\n*   **Page Function**: Visualizing the cutting power.\n*   **Visual Description**: The shaver head cutting through abstract metallic stubble or generating a \"wind\" effect to show motor speed. Dynamic motion blur.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Side Text: \"双环刀网\" / \"DUAL-RING MESH\".\n    *   Data: \"9000 RPM 强劲动力 / High Speed Motor\".\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Dynamic shot, [dual-head shaver] with motion blur effects indicating high speed rotation, sparks or wind visual effects, dark background, energetic composition.\n\n**07. POSTER 07 | PACKAGING/PORTABILITY**\n*   **Page Function**: Gift attribute and size.\n*   **Visual Description**: The shaver placed next to a sleek black gift box, or sliding into a jeans pocket. Emphasize the small size (pebble shape).\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Title: \"一手掌握\" / \"PALM SIZED\".\n*   **Prompt (English)**: [Compact chrome shaver] being slipped into a denim pocket or sitting next to a premium matte black gift box, showcasing small portable size, realistic lighting.\n\n**08. POSTER 08 | MOODBOARD**\n*   **Page Function**: Color and aesthetics.\n*   **Visual Description**: Left: The Shaver. Right: Color swatches (Chrome Silver, Neon Orange, Deep Black) and tech icons.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Top Title: \"赛博美学 / CYBER AESTHETICS\".\n    *   Labels: \"极光银 / Aurora Silver\", \"活力橙 / Vitality Orange\".\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Knolling photography, flat lay, moodboard style, [liquid chrome shaver], color palettes of silver and neon orange, tech accessories, organized layout, clean dark background.\n\n**09. POSTER 09 | SPECIFICATIONS**\n*   **Page Function**: Data sheet.\n*   **Visual Description**: Clean dark grey background with faint tech lines.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Title: \"产品参数 / SPECIFICATIONS\".\n    *   Table:\n        | 产品材质 / Material | ABS + Chrome Plating |\n        | 续航时间 / Battery Life | 60 Minutes |\n        | 充电接口 / Port | Type-C Fast Charge |\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Clean dark grey background, subtle cyber grid lines, minimalist layout for text overlay, empty center space.\n\n**10. POSTER 10 | TRUST & CARE**\n*   **Page Function**: Warranty and box contents.\n*   **Visual Description**: Minimalist icon array on dark background.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Title: \"无忧售后 / WARRANTY\".\n    *   Icons: 1. [Box] 1 Year Warranty; 2. [Truck] Fast Shipping; 3. [Refresh] 30 Days Return.\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Minimalist layout, dark background, space for icons and text, professional and trustworthy vibe.\n",
  "seadream_cn": "**[识别报告]**\n**品牌信息**：无品牌标识/极简风格。视觉核心为蓝色“96”数显与底部橙色“微笑”灯带。\n**核心卖点**：1. 鹅卵石便携造型。 2. “液态金属”未来感电镀工艺。 3. 智能电量数显。 4. 双头浮动剃须。\n**物理属性**：高光镜面电镀铬、亮黑亚克力、哑光黑色罗纹聚合物底座。\n**目标受众**：科技发烧友、差旅商务人士、Z世代潮流男性。\n\n**[风格策略定义]**\n**视觉风格**：赛博未来风 (Tech/Cyber) - 利用深色背景衬托金属光泽与霓虹灯效。\n**排版系统**：玻璃拟态卡片 (Glassmorphism) - 半透明质感契合产品的通透光泽。\n\n---\n\n**00、LOGO生成**\n*   **页面名称**：品牌标识 (Brand Identity)\n*   **设计思路**：现代、冷峻、男性化。\n*   **Prompt**：为品牌“CYBER SHAVE”设计未来感字母Logo，金属银色质感，霓虹橙色发光轮廓，暗黑背景，矢量图，极简，线条利落。\n\n---\n\n**01、海报01｜主KV (Hero Shot) - 强视觉冲击**\n*   **页面功能**：建立第一印象，极致展现液态金属质感。\n*   **画面描述**：9:16竖版。赛博科技风。戏剧性的边缘光勾勒出产品流动的金属曲面和底部橙色灯带。产品悬浮在深邃的空间中，镜面反射出环境光。严格还原产品：鹅卵石造型，镜面银身，蓝色96数显。\n*   **文案与排版**：\n    *   左上角：Logo (小号)。\n    *   主标题(中上)：\"未来锋芒\" (大号黑体) 堆叠 \"LIQUID CHROME\" (小号无衬线)。\n    *   核心文案(玻璃拟态)：[图标] 迷你便携 / [图标] 智能数显。\n    *   CTA按钮(右下)：\"立即抢购 / Shop Now →\"。\n*   **Prompt (English)**：9:16 vertical, Tech Cyberpunk style, cinematic lighting, floating [compact electric shaver with liquid metal chrome finish and wave-like surface, blue 96 digital display, orange LED strip on black ribbed base], dark futuristic background, reflections, high contrast, text overlay instructions. Strictly restore the uploaded product image features.\n*   **Negative**：matte finish, wrong shape, bulky, white background, low res, distorted text.\n\n**02、海报02｜场景展示 (Lifestyle)**\n*   **页面功能**：情感共鸣，代入精致生活场景。\n*   **画面描述**：一位穿着时尚的年轻男士在现代极简浴室或豪华车内，手持这款银色剃须刀。镜面机身倒映着周围环境。营造高端、利落的氛围。\n*   **文案与排版**：\n    *   左下大标题：\"随行所欲\" / \"SHAVE ANYWHERE\"。\n    *   场景说明：\"口袋里的理容专家 / Pocket-sized grooming expert\"。\n*   **Prompt (English)**：Photorealistic lifestyle shot, handsome man holding [compact liquid chrome shaver], modern luxury bathroom setting or car interior, sharp focus on product, reflection on chrome surface, masculine atmosphere, cinematic lighting.\n\n**03、海报03｜多场景/多角度拼贴 (Collage)**\n*   **页面功能**：展示双头刀网与机身侧面线条。\n*   **画面描述**：极简拼贴布局。上方展示顶部双刀头特写，下方展示侧面橙色灯带的流线型设计。背景为暗色科技网格。\n*   **文案与排版**：\n    *   底部标题：\"双面绅士 / DUAL CHARACTER\"。\n    *   列表文案：1. 智能数显 / Smart Display；2. 强劲动力 / Turbo Motor；3. 水洗机身 / Washable。\n*   **Prompt (English)**：Product collage, split screen, [top view of dual-head shaver] and [side view of chrome body with orange light], dark technical grid background, high resolution, 8k.\n\n**04、海报04｜细节01 - 核心卖点/材质 (Close-up)**\n*   **页面功能**：放大材质质感，建立品质信任。\n*   **画面描述**：微距摄影。极度聚焦于机身起伏的波浪纹理和电镀层。反射出抽象的霓虹光影，强调“液态金属”的高级触感。\n*   **文案与排版**：\n    *   指向性标注：\"流体银工艺\" / \"LIQUID SILVER FINISH\"。\n    *   描述文案：\"如液态金属般流动光泽 / Fluid aesthetic like molten metal\"。\n*   **Prompt (English)**：Macro shot, extreme close-up of [liquid metal chrome texture of the shaver], wave-like surface modeling, reflection of neon lights, high gloss, premium material detail.\n\n**05、海报05｜细节02 - 工艺/设计 (Craftsmanship)**\n*   **页面功能**：展示智能科技属性。\n*   **画面描述**：特写拍摄正面黑色中岛区域。蓝色的“96”数字显示清晰锐利，电源键周围有微光。科技感十足。\n*   **文案与排版**：\n    *   居中标题：\"智能数显\" / \"SMART MONITOR\"。\n    *   功能说明：\"电量一目了然 / Battery level at a glance\"。\n*   **Prompt (English)**：Close-up of [glossy black panel with blue 7-segment LED battery display showing number 96], distinct circular power button, high tech feel, dark environment.\n\n**06、海报06｜细节03 - 功能可视化 (Function)**\n*   **页面功能**：通过视觉特效展示强劲动力。\n*   **画面描述**：双环刀网特写，周围带有动态模糊或气流特效，暗示刀头高速旋转的切割力。背景暗黑，火花或蓝色光效点缀。\n*   **文案与排版**：\n    *   侧边文字：\"双环刀网\" / \"DUAL-RING MESH\"。\n    *   数据/说明：\"9000 RPM 强劲动力 / High Speed Motor\"。\n*   **Prompt (English)**：Dynamic shot, [dual-head shaver] with motion blur effects indicating high speed rotation, sparks or wind visual effects, dark background, energetic composition.\n\n**07、海报07｜细节04 - 包装/便携性 (Packaging)**\n*   **页面功能**：展示小巧体积与礼品属性。\n*   **画面描述**：产品正滑入牛仔裤口袋，或放置在一个精致的黑色礼盒旁。强调其如同鹅卵石般的握持感和便携性。\n*   **文案与排版**：\n    *   标题：\"一手掌握\" / \"PALM SIZED\"。\n*   **Prompt (English)**：[Compact chrome shaver] being slipped into a denim pocket or sitting next to a premium matte black gift box, showcasing small portable size, realistic lighting.\n\n**08、海报08｜配色/情绪板 (Moodboard)**\n*   **页面功能**：展示品牌美学与赛博格调。\n*   **画面描述**：左侧产品图，右侧提取的色卡（镜面银、霓虹橙、深邃黑）以及科技风扁平图标（如电池、芯片）。\n*   **文案与排版**：\n    *   顶部标题：\"赛博美学 / CYBER AESTHETICS\"。\n    *   色卡标注：\"极光银 / Aurora Silver\"、\"活力橙 / Vitality Orange\"。\n*   **Prompt (English)**：Knolling photography, flat lay, moodboard style, [liquid chrome shaver], color palettes of silver and neon orange, tech accessories, organized layout, clean dark background.\n\n**09、海报09｜参数/规格 (Specifications)**\n*   **页面功能**：理性信息展示。\n*   **画面描述**：干净的深灰色背景，带有淡淡的科技网格线。\n*   **文案与排版**：\n    *   表格标题：\"参数规格 / SPECIFICATIONS\"。\n    *   表格内容：\n        | 产品材质 / Material | ABS + 电镀铬 |\n        | 续航时间 / Battery Life | 60 分钟 |\n        | 充电接口 / Port | Type-C 快充 |\n*   **Prompt (English)**：Clean dark grey background, subtle cyber grid lines, minimalist layout for text overlay, empty center space.\n\n**10、海报10｜信任/售后 (Trust & Care)**\n*   **页面功能**：消除购买顾虑。\n*   **画面描述**：极简深色背景，线性白色图标阵列。\n*   **文案与排版**：\n    *   标题：\"无忧售后 / WARRANTY\"。\n    *   图标文案：\n        1. [图标] 1年质保 / 1 Year Warranty\n        2. [图标] 极速发货 / Fast Shipping\n        3. [图标] 30天退换 / 30 Days Return\n*   **Prompt (English)**：Minimalist layout, dark background, space for icons and text, professional and trustworthy vibe.\n",
  "layout_logic": "整体采用深色模式（Dark Mode），背景以深灰或纯黑为主，辅以微妙的网格线或光晕，最大程度衬托产品的【镜面银色】反光和【橙色/蓝色】灯光效果。排版建议使用无衬线字体（如 Helvetica Now 或 Roboto），字重对比要强烈（大标题极粗，说明文案极细）。各模块之间建议保持 20px-40px 的黑色呼吸间隔，形成“悬浮卡片”的视觉流，强化未来的科技感。"
}

