  "nano_banana_en": "**[Analysis Report]**\n- **Brand**: Unknown (Implied 'FutureTech' vibe), No explicit text logo, relies on Cyan Digital Display.\n- **USP**: Liquid-metal aesthetics, Ultra-compact portability, Digital battery visualization, Type-C fast charging.\n- **Materials**: High-gloss silver chrome, matte black polymer, emissive orange LED, cyan LED.\n- **Target Audience**: Gen Z men, business travelers, tech gadget enthusiasts.\n- **Visual Style Selection**: **Tech/Cyber (Future Chrome)** - emphasizing the metallic fluidity and neon accents.\n- **Typography Selection**: **Glassmorphism & Bold Sans** - modern, sleek, digital feel.\n\n---\n\n**00、LOGO GENERATION**\n* **Page Name**: Brand Identity\n* **Design Concept**: Cyber-minimalism symbol representing speed and precision.\n* **Prompt**: Cyberpunk logo design for brand \"ChromeShave\", abstract razor blade combined with lightning bolt, silver and neon cyan color scheme, vector, minimal, clean dark grey background.\n\n---\n\n**01、Poster 01 | Main KV (Hero Shot) - High Impact**\n* **Page Function**: Establish the \"Liquid Metal\" premium feel.\n* **Visual Description**: 9:16 vertical. Tech/Cyber style. Studio lighting with cool blue rim light and warm orange reflections matching the device's LED. The silver chrome shaver floats in the center, tilted 45 degrees to show the fluid ridges and the orange light strip. Background is a deep, dark tech void with subtle metallic ripples.\n* **Text & UI Layout**:\n    * Top Left: Logo (Small).\n    * Main Title (Center-Top): \"液态未来\" (Large Bold) stacked \"LIQUID METAL FUTURE\" (Small).\n    * Core Copy (Glass Card): 智能屏显 / Smart Display; type-C快充 / Fast Charge.\n    * CTA (Bottom Right): \"立即购买 / Shop Now →\".\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, Tech/Cyber style, cinematic lighting, [Subject Lock], floating in dark void, blue rim light, orange reflections, high-gloss silver chrome texture, liquid metal aesthetic, text overlay: 'LIQUID METAL FUTURE', clean composition.\n* **Negative Prompt**: cluttered, busy, distorted text, wrong logo, low res, dull metal, rusty.\n\n**02、Poster 02 | Lifestyle Scene**\n* **Page Function**: Emotional connection for the modern traveler.\n* **Visual Description**: A modern, high-tech hotel bathroom or a first-class airplane cabin sink. A well-groomed young man holds the shaver (chrome shell reflecting the environment). Focus on the compact size in hand.\n* **Text & UI Layout**:\n    * Bottom Left Title: \"掌控随心\" / \"CONTROL FREEDOM\".\n    * Scene Copy: \"随时随地，保持锋芒 / Stay Sharp Anywhere\".\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, photorealistic, [Subject Lock], held by hand of young businessman, luxury hotel bathroom background, marble textures, soft morning light, reflection on chrome body, depth of field.\n\n**03、Poster 03 | Collage/Angles**\n* **Page Function**: Showcasing versatility and form factor.\n* **Visual Description**: Minimalist grid layout. Top half: Top view showing the two foil heads. Bottom left: Side profile showing the orange light strip. Bottom right: Bottom view showing USB-C port.\n* **Text & UI Layout**:\n    * Bottom Title: \"全维精工 / Precision Craft\".\n    * List: 1.双刀头 / Dual Head; 2.流光灯带 / LED Strip; 3.便携机身 / Compact Body.\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, collage layout, [Subject Lock], multiple angles, top view of foil heads, side view of orange LED, bottom view of USB-C, clean grey background, studio product photography.\n\n**04、Poster 04 | Detail 01 - Material (Close-up)**\n* **Page Function**: Emphasize the liquid chrome texture.\n* **Visual Description**: Macro shot. Extreme close-up of the silver chrome ridges. The metal looks like flowing water frozen in time. Reflection of a neon light on the curve.\n* **Text & UI Layout**:\n    * Pointer Line: \"液态银电镀\" / \"Liquid Silver Chrome\".\n    * Description: \"流体美学，触感温润 / Fluid Aesthetics, Smooth Touch\".\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, Macro shot, extreme close-up of [Subject Lock] chrome ridges, liquid metal texture, mirror polish, high contrast reflections, premium material visualization.\n\n**05、Poster 05 | Detail 02 - Design/Display**\n* **Page Function**: Highlight the smart display feature.\n* **Visual Description**: Close-up on the central matte black pill shape. The cyan \"96\" is glowing brightly. The circular button has a subtle tactile texture.\n* **Text & UI Layout**:\n    * Center Title: \"智能数显\" / \"SMART DIGITAL DISPLAY\".\n    * Function Note: \"电量一目了然 / Battery at a Glance\".\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, close-up of [Subject Lock] central black panel, glowing cyan digital number '96', matte black texture contrast with silver, tech interface style.\n\n**06、Poster 06 | Detail 03 - Function (Motor/Power)**\n* **Page Function**: Visualizing the hidden power/speed.\n* **Visual Description**: The shaver head is surrounded by abstract \"wind\" or motion blur lines (cyan color) to suggest high-speed motor rotation. 8000 RPM visualization.\n* **Text & UI Layout**:\n    * Side Text: \"强劲动力\" / \"POWERFUL MOTOR\".\n    * Data: \"8000 转/分钟 / RPM\".\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, [Subject Lock], motion blur effects around shaving heads, cyan speed lines, visualizing air flow, high-speed motor concept, tech infographic style.\n\n**07、Poster 07 | Packaging/Portability**\n* **Page Function**: Demonstrating travel readiness.\n* **Visual Description**: The shaver is half-inserted into a sleek, dark denim pocket or a premium leather travel pouch. The orange light strip peeks out slightly.\n* **Text & UI Layout**:\n    * Title: \"口袋精灵\" / \"POCKET COMPANION\".\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, [Subject Lock] placed inside a dark denim pocket, compact size demonstration, fashion photography style, convenient travel concept.\n\n**08、Poster 08 | Moodboard**\n* **Page Function**: Color and aesthetic inspiration.\n* **Visual Description**: Knolling layout. The shaver in center. Surrounded by silver spheres, a piece of obsidian (black), a neon orange tube, and a cyber-blue glass chip.\n* **Text & UI Layout**:\n    * Top Title: \"赛博美学 / Cyber Aesthetics\".\n    * Color Labels: \"铬银 / Chrome\", \"幻影黑 / Phantom Black\", \"极光橙 / Aurora Orange\".\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, Knolling photography, flat lay, moodboard style, [Subject Lock] center, silver spheres, obsidian rock, neon orange tube, cyber blue glass, clean arrangement.\n\n**09、Poster 09 | Specifications**\n* **Page Function**: Technical specs table.\n* **Visual Description**: Clean dark grey background with subtle circuit board patterns (very faint).\n* **Text & UI Layout**:\n    * Table Title: \"参数规格 / Specifications\".\n    * Content:\n        | 充电接口 / Port | USB Type-C |\n        | 续航时间 / Battery | 60 Days |\n        | 防水等级 / Waterproof | IPX7 |\n        | 机身材质 / Material | Chrome/ABS |\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, Clean dark tech background, minimal layout, empty space for text, subtle geometric lines.\n\n**10、Poster 10 | Trust & Care**\n* **Page Function**: Warranty and contents.\n* **Visual Description**: Minimalist dark background with neon outline icons.\n* **Text & UI Layout**:\n    * Title: \"无忧售后 / Worry-Free\".\n    * Icons: 1.[Box Icon] 礼盒包装; 2.[Shield Icon] 一年质保; 3.[Truck Icon] 极速发货.\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, Minimalist neon outline icons layout, dark background, tech support concept, clean UI.",
  "seadream_cn": "**[识别报告]**\n- **品牌基因**: 隐形科技感，无Logo极简主义，赛博朋克美学。\n- **核心卖点**: 液态金属流线机身、Type-C快充便携、可视电量数显、悬浮感橙色光效。\n- **材质指纹**: 高光镀铬银(High-gloss Chrome) + 哑光黑(Matte Black) + 荧光橙/青(Neon Accents)。\n- **受众画像**: Z世代潮流男性、极客、商务差旅人士。\n- **风格决策**: **未来科技风 (Cyber Tech)** - 强调光影流动与金属质感。\n- **排版系统**: **玻璃拟态 + 粗体无衬线** - 营造通透的高级科技感。\n\n---\n\n**00、LOGO生成**\n* **页面名称**：品牌标识 (Brand Identity)\n* **设计思路**：结合闪电与刀片元素的抽象符号，银蓝配色，体现速度与锋利。\n* **Prompt**：[Cyberpunk Style] logo design for brand \"ChromeShave\", abstract razor symbol, silver and neon cyan, vector, minimal.\n\n---\n\n**01、海报01｜主KV (Hero Shot) - 强视觉冲击**\n* **页面功能**：确立“液态金属”的高级视觉调性。\n* **画面描述**：9:16竖版。深邃的科技黑背景，主体剃须刀悬浮于画面中央，略微倾斜。一道冷蓝色轮廓光勾勒出银色机身的流体线条，底部橙色呼吸灯带在黑暗中熠熠生辉，形成冷暖对比。\n* **文案与排版**：\n    * 左上角：Logo (小号)。\n    * 主标题(中上)：\"液态未来\" (大号黑体) 堆叠 \"LIQUID METAL FUTURE\" (小号)。\n    * 核心文案(玻璃拟态卡片)：智能屏显 / Smart Display；Type-C快充 / Fast Charge。\n    * CTA按钮(右下)：\"立即购买 / Shop Now →\"。\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, Cyberpunk style, [Subject Lock], floating in dark void, cinematic lighting, blue rim light, orange LED glow, liquid metal silver texture, sharp focus, masterpiece.\n* **Negative Prompt**: cluttered, busy, distorted text, wrong logo, low res, plastic texture.\n\n**02、海报02｜场景展示 (Lifestyle)**\n* **页面功能**：代入感，展示商务差旅场景下的精致体验。\n* **画面描述**：高端酒店洗漱台，大理石台面。一位穿着白衬衫的年轻男士手持剃须刀（仅露手部和袖口），剃须刀的镜面机身反射出周围的环境光，显得晶莹剔透。\n* **文案与排版**：\n    * 左下大标题：\"掌控随心\" / \"CONTROL FREEDOM\"。\n    * 场景说明：\"随时随地，保持锋芒 / Stay Sharp Anywhere\"。\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, photorealistic, [Subject Lock] held by man's hand, white shirt cuff, luxury hotel bathroom, marble counter, reflection, elegant atmosphere.\n\n**03、海报03｜多场景/多角度拼贴 (Collage)**\n* **页面功能**：全方位展示机身细节与结构。\n* **画面描述**：极简深灰背景拼贴。上方大图为俯视双刀头特写；左下为侧面橙色灯带特写；右下为底部Type-C接口特写。\n* **文案与排版**：\n    * 底部标题：\"全维精工 / Precision Craft\"。\n    * 列表文案：1.双刀头 / Dual Head；2.流光灯带 / LED Strip；3.便携机身 / Compact Body。\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, collage layout, [Subject Lock], top view, side view, bottom view, clean grey background, studio lighting.\n\n**04、海报04｜细节01 - 核心卖点/材质 (Close-up)**\n* **页面功能**：放大“液态银”的极致工艺。\n* **画面描述**：微距摄影。聚焦于机身表面的流体棱脊，银色镀铬材质呈现出流动的水银质感，高光处有星芒闪烁。\n* **文案与排版**：\n    * 指向性标注：\"液态银电镀\" / \"Liquid Silver Chrome\"。\n    * 描述文案：\"流体美学，触感温润 / Fluid Aesthetics, Smooth Touch\"。\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, Macro shot, close-up of [Subject Lock] chrome surface, liquid metal texture, fluid ridges, high gloss, reflection, premium detail.\n\n**05、海报05｜细节02 - 工艺/设计 (Craftsmanship)**\n* **页面功能**：强调智能交互体验。\n* **画面描述**：特写中央黑色胶囊区域。青色LED数字“96”在黑色背景下清晰发光，圆形凹槽按键展现出细腻的磨砂质感。\n* **文案与排版**：\n    * 居中标题：\"智能数显\" / \"SMART DIGITAL DISPLAY\"。\n    * 功能说明：\"电量一目了然 / Battery at a Glance\"。\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, close-up of [Subject Lock] central panel, cyan digital display '96', matte black texture, tech interface aesthetic.\n\n**06、海报06｜细节03 - 功能可视化 (Function)**\n* **页面功能**：视觉化呈现强劲动力。\n* **画面描述**：剃须刀头部周围环绕着青色的旋风特效线条，象征刀头的高速旋转与切割力。\n* **文案与排版**：\n    * 侧边文字：\"强劲动力\" / \"POWERFUL MOTOR\"。\n    * 数据/说明：\"8000 转/分钟 / RPM\"。\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, [Subject Lock], cyan motion blur lines, wind effect around shaving head, speed visualization, high-tech motor concept.\n\n**07、海报07｜细节04 - 包装/便携性 (Packaging)**\n* **页面功能**：展示极致便携属性。\n* **画面描述**：剃须刀被轻松放入一条深色牛仔裤的口袋中，只露出顶部边缘和一点橙色光条，体现小巧体积。\n* **文案与排版**：\n    * 标题：\"口袋精灵\" / \"POCKET COMPANION\"。\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, [Subject Lock] inside jeans pocket, showing compact size, lifestyle photography, convenient carry.\n\n**08、海报08｜配色/情绪板 (Moodboard)**\n* **页面功能**：传达赛博朋克设计美学。\n* **画面描述**：Knolling平铺风格。剃须刀居中，周围摆放银色金属球、黑色黑曜石、橙色霓虹灯管、青色玻璃片。\n* **文案与排版**：\n    * 顶部标题：\"赛博美学 / Cyber Aesthetics\"。\n    * 色卡标注：\"铬银 / Chrome\"、\"幻影黑 / Phantom Black\"、\"极光橙 / Aurora Orange\"。\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, Knolling style, [Subject Lock], silver spheres, obsidian, neon orange tube, cyber blue glass, flat lay, artistic arrangement.\n\n**09、海报09｜参数/规格 (Specifications)**\n* **页面功能**：清晰展示硬件参数。\n* **画面描述**：极简深色科技背景，带有若隐若现的电路纹理。\n* **文案与排版**：\n    * 表格标题：\"参数规格 / Specifications\"。\n    * 表格内容：\n        | 充电接口 / Port | USB Type-C |\n        | 续航时间 / Battery | 60 Days |\n        | 防水等级 / Waterproof | IPX7 |\n        | 机身材质 / Material | Chrome/ABS |\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, Dark tech background, subtle circuit pattern, clean space for text.\n\n**10、海报10｜信任/售后 (Trust & Care)**\n* **页面功能**：售后保障承诺。\n* **画面描述**：深色背景，排列三个霓虹线条风格的图标。\n* **文案与排版**：\n    * 标题：\"无忧售后 / Worry-Free\"。\n    * 图标文案：\n        1. [礼盒图标] 礼盒包装\n        2. [盾牌图标] 一年质保\n        3. [卡车图标] 极速发货\n* **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, Neon outline icons, dark background, clean UI layout.",
  "layout_logic": "建议采用深色系（Dark Mode）长图设计。1. **首屏视觉流**：利用产品底部的橙色灯带作为视觉引导线，贯穿首屏到第二屏。2. **材质对比**：由于产品主要是高光银色，背景建议使用深邃的哑光黑或带有细腻噪点的深灰，以凸显产品的液态光泽。3. **文字层级**：所有中文主标题建议使用带有未来感的宽黑体（如Oppo Sans或优设标题黑），英文使用等宽字体（Monospaced）增加极客感。4. **光影呼应**：在每张海报的角落，可以添加轻微的青色或橙色光晕，呼应产品的双色LED特征。"
