  "nano_banana_en": "[ANALYSIS REPORT]\n**Brand Info**: Unbranded Luxury / Bridal Boutique Style. Logo strategy: Elegant serif monogram or script font (e.g., 'Royal Bride').\n**USP**: 1. Baroque Court Style (Vintage Opulence). 2. High-refraction Crystal Pavé (Diamond-like Sparkle). 3. Full Bridal Coordination (3-Piece Set).\n**Materials**: Silver-plated alloy, high-clarity cubic zirconia/crystal glass.\n**Audience**: Brides-to-be, pageant contestants, prom attendees, formal event guests (Age 20-35).\n**Style Strategy**: \"Romantic Royal\" - Soft lighting, tulle textures, bokeh effects, high-key photography to emphasize sparkle.\n**Typography**: Elegant Serif (e.g., Playfair Display) paired with thin Sans-serif for details.\n\n---\n\n**00. LOGO GENERATION**\n*   **Page Name**: Brand Identity\n*   **Design Logic**: Luxurious and wedding-appropriate.\n*   **Prompt**: Elegant luxury logo design for jewelry brand \"Royal Bride\", intertwining serif letters, silver foil texture, white background, vector, minimal, high fashion style.\n\n---\n\n**01. POSTER 01 | Hero Shot**\n*   **Page Function**: First Impression & Core Aesthetics\n*   **Visual Description**: 9:16 Vertical. Romantic Royal style. Soft, dreamy lighting hitting the crystals to create starburst flares. The 3-piece set is arranged artistically on a white silk or tulle surface. The tiara stands upright in the back, necklace draped in a V-shape in front, earrings placed symmetrically. \n> Strict Subject Lock: Silver-tone Baroque scrollwork set defined by heavy pavé encrustation and prominent vertical pear-cut crystal focal points.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Top Center: Logo (Small).\n    *   Main Title (Center): \"加冕时刻\" (Large Serif) stacked on \"CROWNING MOMENT\" (Small Sans).\n    *   Core Features (Bottom Left): Crystal Pavé / 密镶工艺 ; Baroque Style / 巴洛克风.\n    *   CTA (Bottom Right): \"Shop Now →\".\n*   **Prompt (English)**: 9:16 vertical, Romantic Royal style, soft studio lighting, starburst bokeh, 3-piece bridal jewelry set (tiara, necklace, earrings) arranged on white silk, strictly restore silver-tone Baroque scrollwork and pear-cut crystals, text overlay \"CROWNING MOMENT\", elegant atmosphere, 8k resolution.\n*   **Negative**: gold, yellow metal, colored stones, dark background, messy arrangement.\n\n---\n\n**02. POSTER 02 | Lifestyle/Scene**\n*   **Page Function**: Emotional Resonance\n*   **Visual Description**: A beautiful bride wearing the tiara and earrings, looking down slightly with a soft smile. Soft focus background of a wedding veil or floral arch. Natural light illuminating her face and the jewelry sparkle.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Bottom Left Title: \"主角光环\" / \"SPOTLIGHT READY\".\n    *   Scene Text: \"让每一个转身都璀璨夺目 / Sparkle at every turn\".\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Beautiful bride model wearing silver crystal tiara and dangle earrings, soft wedding makeup, white veil background, dreamy lighting, depth of field, strictly restore jewelry design, high fashion photography, emotional connection.\n\n---\n\n**03. POSTER 03 | Collage**\n*   **Page Function**: Versatility & Angles\n*   **Visual Description**: Minimalist grid layout. Top half: The necklace draped on a mannequin neck. Bottom left: Close up of the earring. Bottom right: The tiara placed on a velvet cushion.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Center Title: \"奢华套装 / LUXURY SET\".\n    *   List: 1. 皇冠 / Tiara ; 2. 项链 / Necklace ; 3. 耳环 / Earrings.\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Collage layout, white background, distinct sections showing necklace on mannequin, earring close-up, and tiara on cushion, strictly restore silver pear-cut crystal details, clean editorial design.\n\n---\n\n**04. POSTER 04 | Close-up (Material)**\n*   **Page Function**: Quality Assurance (Sparkle)\n*   **Visual Description**: Extreme macro shot of the central pear-cut crystal on the tiara. capturing the facets and the surrounding pavé stones. High contrast reflection to show clarity.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Pointer Line: \"5A级锆石\" / \"5A Cubic Zirconia\".\n    *   Description: \"钻石般纯净火彩 / Diamond-like Brilliance\".\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Macro shot, extreme close-up of central pear-cut crystal on silver tiara, visible facets and light refraction, sharp focus, metallic texture, luxury jewelry photography.\n\n---\n\n**05. POSTER 05 | Craftsmanship**\n*   **Page Function**: Design Details\n*   **Visual Description**: Close up of the metal scrollwork (back or side view) showing the prong settings and the smooth silver plating. Emphasize the sturdy structure.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Center Title: \"精工镶嵌\" / \"EXQUISITE CRAFT\".\n    *   Description: \"手工爪镶，稳固防掉钻 / Hand-set prongs, secure and durable\".\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Close-up of silver metal scrollwork and prong settings, high key lighting, smooth plating texture, technical detail shot, strictly restore baroque pattern.\n\n---\n\n**06. POSTER 06 | Function (Fit)**\n*   **Page Function**: Comfort & Wearability\n*   **Visual Description**: A side profile of a model or a mannequin head showing the tiara's curvature fitting perfectly on the head, or the necklace lying flat against the collarbone.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Side Text: \"人体工学设计\" / \"ERGONOMIC FIT\".\n    *   Data: \"贴合头型 不易滑落 / Fits securely and comfortably\".\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Side profile shot, tiara fitting curve of head, necklace lying flat on collarbone, clean background, focus on fit and structure, white styling.\n\n---\n\n**07. POSTER 07 | Packaging**\n*   **Page Function**: Gifting Attribute\n*   **Visual Description**: The jewelry set placed neatly inside a premium velvet jewelry box (navy blue or black) with the lid open. A ribbon lies next to it.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Title: \"臻美礼盒\" / \"PREMIUM GIFT BOX\".\n    *   Sub: \"婚礼/送礼首选 / Perfect for Weddings & Gifts\".\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Premium open jewelry box with velvet interior containing the 3-piece silver crystal set, ribbon prop, soft luxury lighting, gift giving atmosphere.\n\n---\n\n**08. POSTER 08 | Moodboard**\n*   **Page Function**: Aesthetic Inspiration\n*   **Visual Description**: Left side: The jewelry set. Right side: Circular swatches of silver texture, crystal facets, and white lace/satin fabric texture.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Top Title: \"灵感美学 / AESTHETICS\".\n    *   Tags: \"纯净银 / Pure Silver\", \"璀璨晶 / Sparkling Crystal\".\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Moodboard style, knolling photography, jewelry set on left, texture swatches of silver and lace on right, elegant color palette, editorial design.\n\n---\n\n**09. POSTER 09 | Specifications**\n*   **Page Function**: Rational Information\n*   **Visual Description**: Clean light grey background. The jewelry items are isolated with slight shadows.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Title: \"产品参数 / SPECIFICATIONS\".\n    *   Table:\n        | 材质 Material | 镀银合金 + 锆石 / Silver Plated + CZ |\n        | 包含 Included | 皇冠+项链+耳环 / Tiara+Necklace+Earrings |\n        | 风格 Style | 欧式宫廷 / Baroque Royal |\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Clean studio shot of jewelry items isolated on light grey background, minimal shadows, ready for text overlay.\n\n---\n\n**10. POSTER 10 | Trust & Care**\n*   **Page Function**: After-sales & Maintenance\n*   **Visual Description**: Minimalist icons (diamond, cloth, box) on a white background.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**:\n    *   Title: \"保养建议 / CARE GUIDE\".\n    *   Icons: 1. 避免潮湿 / Avoid Moisture; 2. 软布擦拭 / Soft Cloth Wipe; 3. 密封保存 / Sealed Storage.\n*   **Prompt (English)**: Minimalist layout, soft icons representing jewelry care, white background, clean and professional look.",
  "seadream_cn": "【识别报告】\n基于视觉指纹分析，该产品为典型的“巴洛克宫廷风”三件套（皇冠+项链+耳环）。核心视觉特征是银色金属基底、复杂卷草纹（Scrollwork）以及标志性的梨形（水滴状）主钻。\n**风格定调**：SeaDream 4.5 建议采用“梦幻婚礼 (Dreamy Wedding)”风格。画面需强调晶莹剔透的光泽感与神圣的仪式感，背景多用柔光、白纱、花影，以衬托银色饰品的纯净。\n\n---\n\n**00、LOGO设计**\n*   **页面名称**：品牌印记\n*   **画面意境**：高端定制感，银色烫金质感，配合极简线条。\n*   **中文指令**：奢华珠宝品牌Logo设计，品牌名“Royal Bride”，衬线字体，银色金属质感，白色背景，极简高贵。\n\n---\n\n**01、海报01｜主KV - 璀璨加冕**\n*   **页面功能**：视觉定锚，瞬间抓住准新娘眼球。\n*   **画面意境**：9:16竖构图。柔和的晨光洒在丝绸台面上，三件套错落有致。皇冠位于高处，项链呈心形环绕，光线在梨形主钻上折射出迷人的星芒。\n*   **文案布局**：\n    *   顶部居中：Logo。\n    *   核心大标题：『 加冕时刻 』 (思源宋体 Heavy) \n    *   副标题：CROWNING MOMENT\n    *   卖点修饰：巴洛克宫廷风 | 5A级璀璨锆石\n    *   底部按钮：立即购买 →\n\n---\n\n**02、海报02｜场景 - 婚礼梦境**\n*   **页面功能**：代入感，唤起对婚礼的憧憬。\n*   **画面意境**：身穿洁白婚纱的新娘侧影，头戴皇冠，耳畔垂着闪耀的耳环。背景是虚化的教堂光影或唯美的鲜花拱门。她低眉浅笑，光影温柔地勾勒出她幸福的轮廓。\n*   **文案布局**：\n    *   左下悬浮文字：『 主角光环 』 / SPOTLIGHT READY\n    *   描述：让每一个转身，都惊艳全场。\n\n---\n\n**03、海报03｜拼贴 - 全套展示**\n*   **页面功能**：一目了然展示套装内容。\n*   **画面意境**：极简分割布局。主图展示项链佩戴在模特颈部的特写，辅图分别展示耳环的灵动垂坠感和皇冠的整体造型。\n*   **文案布局**：\n    *   居中标题：『 奢华三件套 』 / LUXURY SET\n    *   清单：1. 灵动皇冠 / Tiara；2. 华丽项链 / Necklace；3. 气质耳环 / Earrings。\n\n---\n\n**04、海报04｜细节 - 极致火彩**\n*   **页面功能**：展示材质的高级感，拒绝廉价感。\n*   **画面意境**：微距镜头直怼皇冠正中央的那颗大水滴主钻。捕捉它内部通透的质感和切割面反射出的七彩火彩。周围的小碎钻如众星捧月般闪耀。\n*   **文案布局**：\n    *   引线标注：『 5A级锆石 』 / 5A Cubic Zirconia\n    *   说明：钻石般纯净，奢华闪耀。\n\n---\n\n**05、海报05｜工艺 - 精工镶嵌**\n*   **页面功能**：体现做工精细，稳固耐用。\n*   **画面意境**：侧拍金属底托的细节，展示流畅的卷草纹路和精细的爪镶工艺。金属表面光滑如镜，没有任何毛刺。\n*   **文案布局**：\n    *   标题：『 精工爪镶 』 / EXQUISITE CRAFT\n    *   说明：手工镶嵌工艺，稳固不易掉钻。\n\n---\n\n**06、海报06｜佩戴 - 舒适贴合**\n*   **页面功能**：消除佩戴不适的顾虑。\n*   **画面意境**：展示皇冠佩戴在发髻上的细节，或者项链顺滑地贴合在锁骨处。强调线条的流畅性与人体工学的结合。\n*   **文案布局**：\n    *   侧边文字：『 人体工学设计 』 / ERGONOMIC FIT\n    *   说明：贴合头型与颈部线条，佩戴舒适。\n\n---\n\n**07、海报07｜包装 - 仪式感**\n*   **页面功能**：强化送礼属性。\n*   **画面意境**：一个深蓝色的丝绒首饰盒打开着，三件套静静躺在里面，旁边散落着几片玫瑰花瓣或一条丝带。灯光聚焦在首饰上。\n*   **文案布局**：\n    *   标题：『 臻美礼盒 』 / PREMIUM GIFT BOX\n    *   副标题：婚礼配饰 / 闺蜜送礼 / 珍藏之选\n\n---\n\n**08、海报08｜美学 - 灵感板**\n*   **页面功能**：提升品牌格调。\n*   **画面意境**：左侧是产品图，右侧排列着银色金属质感图、水滴形状图示、蕾丝纹理图示。色彩统一在银白灰的高级色调中。\n*   **文案布局**：\n    *   标题：『 灵感美学 』 / AESTHETICS\n    *   关键词：纯净银光 · 璀璨晶钻\n\n---\n\n**09、海报09｜参数 - 规格一览**\n*   **页面功能**：提供决策数据。\n*   **画面意境**：干净的灰白渐变背景，产品平铺。\n*   **文案布局**：\n    *   表格标题：『 产品参数 』 / SPECIFICATIONS\n    *   内容填充：\n        | 材质 | 环保合金镀银 + 锆石 |\n        | 包含 | 皇冠 + 项链 + 耳环 |\n        | 风格 | 欧式巴洛克宫廷风 |\n\n---\n\n**10、海报10｜售后 - 无忧承诺**\n*   **页面功能**：建立信任。\n*   **画面意境**：极简线条图标风格。\n*   **文案布局**：\n    *   标题：『 贴心售后 』 / SERVICE\n    *   图标说明：密封保存、避免化学品、软布擦拭。",
