ound, distorted text, wrong shape, colorful body, messy.\n\n---\n\n**02、Poster 02 | Lifestyle Scene**\n*   **Visual Description**: A bright, modern bathroom countertop. Marble texture. A pair of glasses is being placed into the device (silicone collar removed to show steel tank). Water ripples gently inside. Sunlight streaming through a window.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**: \n    *   Bottom Left Title: \"焕新视界\" / \"Refresh Your Vision\".\n    *   Scene Description: \"3分钟快速清洗，重现透亮光泽 / 3-min Quick Clean\".\n*   **Prompt**: 9:16 vertical, lifestyle photography, modern bright bathroom setting, marble countertop, strictly restore the uploaded product image features: white cylindrical body, stainless steel tank revealed (silicone collar removed), grey control panel. A hand holding glasses over the water, gentle water ripples, natural sunlight, high key lighting, photorealistic.\n\n---\n\n**03、Poster 03 | Collage/Versatility**\n*   **Visual Description**: A grid layout. \n    *   Top: Cleaning jewelry (rings/necklaces) in the steel tank.\n    *   Bottom: Cleaning makeup brushes or dentures using the silicone collar mode.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**: \n    *   Center Title: \"一机多用 / Multi-Purpose\".\n    *   List: 1. 眼镜清洗 / Glasses; 2. 首饰护理 / Jewelry; 3. 牙具消毒 / Dental Care.\n*   **Prompt**: 9:16 vertical, split screen collage. Top half: Diamond ring submerged in water inside the stainless steel tank of the white device. Bottom half: Makeup brushes resting in the grey silicone ribbed insert of the device. Clean bright lighting, macro details, sharp focus.\n\n---\n\n**04、Poster 04 | Detail - Tank Material**\n*   **Visual Description**: Extreme close-up of the interior stainless steel tank. Focusing on the \"MAX\" embossed line and the metallic grain of the 304 steel. Water is crystal clear.\n*   **Text & UI Layout**: \n    *   Pointer Line: \"304食品级不锈钢\" / \"304 Food Grade Steel\".\n    *   Description: \"耐腐蚀，易清洁 / Corrosion Resistant\".\n*   **Prompt**: 9:16 vertical, macro photo